# Phase 0 / Plan 01 minimal .gitignore — covers ONLY artifacts produced by the
# Python toolchain bootstrap (uv venv + tool caches). The full project-wide
# .gitignore (credentials, .env, raw FIT files, parquet, mp4 fixtures, etc.)
# is delivered by a separate Phase 0 plan per CONTEXT D-14 / BOOT-07.
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
